  <brief_title>Efficacy of Mefenamic Acid and Hyoscine for Pain Relief During Saline Infusion Sonohysterography in Infertile Women</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy of Mefenamic Acid and Hyoscine for Pain Relief During Saline Infusion Sonohysterography in Infertile Women. A Double Blind Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
