  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  infertility female

          -  no history of HSG or Hysteroscopy

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  vaginal or pelvic infection

          -  abnormal Pap smear

          -  contraindications for Mefenamic acid including upper and lower GI ulcers, bleeding
             disorder, Asthma or allergies, renal disease, using Warfarin,Aspirin, Lithium, history
             of Mefenamic acid or Hyoscine allergies
      </textblock>
